      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "Toggle navigation National Library of Medicine National Library of Medicine Support Center Home Sign in --> NLM Support Center Knowledge Base KA-04188 Print Retrieving NLM bibliographic records from the LocatorPlus Catalog via Z39.50 Views: Retrieving NLM bibliographic records from the LocatorPlus Catalog via Z39.50 NLM provides Z39.50 access to its online public access catalog, LocatorPlus Catalog .&#160; Connection to the catalog via Alma, the NLM library services platform, can be configured with the parameters below: Name:&#160; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; NLM Alma Host:&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; &#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; na91.alma.exlibrisgroup.com Database:&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; 01NLM_INST Port:&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;1921 Syntax:&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; MARC21 The following Z39.50 search options are supported by Alma: Search Field Name Use Attribute Position Attribute Truncation Attribute Personal name 1 1,3 1,100 Title 4 1,3 1,100 ISBN 7 3 1,100 ISSN 8 3 1,100 Local control number 12 1,3 1,100 Subject heading 21 1,3 1,100 Date of publication 31 1,3 1,100 Author 1003 1,3 1,100 Author (personal name) 1004 1,3 1,100 Any keyword 1016 3 1,100 OCLC Number 1211 1,3 1,100 More information on Z39.50 resources is available from the Gateway to Library Catalogs managed by the Library of Congress.",
